      "message": "[Major] Line 2256: SwarmLoaded is emitted before loadMissingBodyOverwrites() runs, so the initial payload sent to clients does not include the plugin body overwrites. Clients will render original bodies first and only later receive SwarmMessageUpdated, which contradicts the ChatHandler API comment saying transforms happen before SwarmLoaded. Apply transforms before emitting SwarmLoaded, or update the API/comment to make the async update behavior explicit.",
