      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 144: transformSwarmMessages() holds ChatServicesManager::mtx_ while invoking plugin code. Plugin transforms can be slow and can call back into registered services that acquire the same mutex, creating the same deadlock pattern this patch fixes elsewhere. Snapshot eligible handlers under the lock, then invoke them outside it.\n```suggestion\nstd::vector\u003cChatHandler*\u003e handlersToTransform;\n{\n    std::lock_guard const lk(mtx_);\n    // populate handlersToTransform using chatHandlerToggled_/allowDenyList_\n}\nfor (auto* handler : handlersToTransform) {\n    handler-\u003etransformSwarmMessages(messages, accountId, conversationId);\n}\n```",
      "revId": "67805d5f8d70aea3f9e25ba0bba0a9ce17262503",
