      "message": "[Critical] Line 239: The service authorization is per-plugin, but the stored value is a single shared pluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"]. clearSwarmBodyOverwrite(), reloadBodyOverwriteConversations(), and updateMessageBodyOverwrite() can overwrite or clear another enabled plugin\u0027s body overwrite in the same conversation. This violates the stated isolation and will cause incorrect UI state when more than one chat plugin transforms bodies. Store overwrites under a plugin-scoped key or keep per-plugin overwrite state and resolve the active value deterministically before emitting updates.",
      "revId": "67805d5f8d70aea3f9e25ba0bba0a9ce17262503",
